Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:52.63,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}Love  for  you  只希望你能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.37,0:20:57.83,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我想要更加温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:21:03.38,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}无法触及你的手的时候
